file.content:
openapi: 3.0.3
info:
  title: open-api-custom API
  version: "1.0"
# tag::adocPath[]
paths:
  /authors/{index}:
    get:
      summary: Returns an author for a given index
# end::adocPath[]
      parameters:
        - name: index
          in: path
          required: true
          schema:
            format: int32
            type: integer
# tag::adocResponse[]
      responses:
        "204":
          description: Author not found
        "200":
          description: Author returned for a given index
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                type: string
# end::adocResponse[]

Error: notImplemented: path "/authors/{index}": get: responses: 200: contents: unsupported content types: [text/plain]
